title: Jenkins and Jonez - How Teenage Kobe Bryant Became Kobe Bryant, With Mike Sielski
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - How Teenage Kobe Bryant Became Kobe Bryant, With Mike Sielski
description:
After discussing PJ Tucker also wearing the fire shirt, Urban Meyer’s latest antics, and why Nancy Regan was trending, the guys talk to reporter Mike Sielski about his new podcast and book about how Kobe Bryant grew into himself.
